welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Pataskala, where small-town charm meets big-city opportunities. Get ready to experience our vibrant community, known for its friendly locals, historic charm, and beautiful parks. We invite you to immerse yourself in all that Pataskala has to offer and make unforgettable memories."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Port Columbus International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A is primarily used for domestic flights operated by American Airlines and its regional partners.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B serves domestic flights operated by Southwest Airlines.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C is used for domestic flights operated by Delta Air Lines and its regional partners.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'CMH Free WiFi' from the list of available networks.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Rickenbacker Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Rickenbacker Airport handles a large volume of freight and is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
